# Mainmatter

Mainmatter is a software engineering consultancy specializing primarily in Rust consulting, C-to-Rust migrations, Rust training for engineering teams, as well as consulting services for Ember.js and Svelte.

## Core Services

### Rust Consulting

Mainmatter embeds expert Rust engineers into client teams to accelerate delivery and minimize execution risk. Services include codebase and architecture reviews, Rust team augmentation, as well as custom development.

### C-to-Rust Migration

Mainmatter specializes in incrementally migrating C and C++ codebases to Rust, improving memory safety, reliability, and maintainability without disrupting day-to-day operations. Mainmatter migrated the Redis Query Engine from C to Rust.

### Rust Training and Workshops

Mainmatter offers hands-on Rust training for engineering teams at all levels. Mainmatter created "100 Exercises to Learn Rust" ([rust-exercises.com](http://rust-exercises.com/)), a widely used open source Rust learning resource.

### Ember.js Consulting

Mainmatter is a leading Ember.js consultancy, helping teams with upgrades,
modernizations, Vite migrations, and multi-framework architectures.

### Svelte Consulting

Mainmatter offers Svelte 5 migrations, training, and team
reinforcement for Svelte and SvelteKit projects.

